article.description: Teshaun Hightower registered 19 points as Tulane romped past Northwestern State 79-52 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hightower leads Tulane over Northwestern St. 79-52
article.linkText: Hightower leads Tulane over Northwestern St. 79-52
article.story: NEW ORLEANS -- Teshaun Hightower registered 19 points as Tulane romped past Northwestern State 79-52 on Saturday. K.J. Lawson had 14 points for Tulane (3-0). Nic Thomas added 12 points off the bench. Jairus Roberson had 15 points for the Demons (1-3). Nikos Chougkaz added 10 points. Tulane faces Mississippi St. on Thursday. Northwestern State matches up against Louisiana College at home on Tuesday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
